title: The Tashkent Files
subTitle: Following the mysterious death of India's second prime minister, Lal Bahadur Shastri, a team launches a probe into the conspiracy of it being an assassination.

subTitle: Jyotin Chatterjee, a former judge, falls for Jenny, a young and independent woman. However, things take a turn when his family scrutinises their relationship.

title: Saheb, Biwi Aur Gangster 3
subTitle: Madhvi Devi relishes her political power but worries about losing it upon her husband Aditya's release from prison. To prevent this, she recruits Uday, a gangster, to assassinate him.

title: Footfairy
subTitle: A CBI officer investigates a string of gruesome murders committed by a serial killer with a foot festish. However, things take an ugly turn when he gets close to catching the killer.

title: Manmarziyaan

subTitle: Jazz, a 40-year-old man, leads a frivolous casanova lifestyle in London. However, when Tia, a young woman claiming to be his daughter, enters his life, he decides to mend his ways.

title: Agni

subTitle: Ayan, a pharmaceutical salesman, decides to stand against his company after discovering that their new baby formula is responsible for the death of many babies..

subTitle: Kabir infiltrates a Maoist organisation to help Adil Khan, who is a decorated police officer and his friend. As he gets deeper into the organisation, Kabir starts sympathising with the group's plight and starts having second thoughts.

subTitle: After his mother is raped one night, Kannu, an eight-year-old boy, writes a letter to the prime minister of India and embarks on a journey from Mumbai to Delhi with his two friends.

title: Crew
subTitle: Three ambitious female cabin attendants from Mumbai get caught in a web of lies during their pursuit of dreams, leading to an unexpected heist.

title: Beyond the Clouds
subTitle: Tara inadvertently sets the wheels in motion for a life-altering, unsavoury occurrence after she seeks help from the wrong person to protect her drug-dealing brother from the police.

subTitle: A recovery agent and a designer become part of a big Bollywood event in New York, where chaos ensues, changing their lives forever.

subTitle: Jaya and Yogi, two contrasting personalities, set out to retrace past relationships, sparking the most eventful trip of their lives.

subTitle: The lives of four individuals - a father, his pilot daughter, a prostitute, and a migrant worker - are thrown into turmoil when the Indian government announces a nationwide lockdown.

subTitle: A rock star, a migrant labourer, a doctor and a policeman find themselves struggling to cope with the ensuing chaos surrounding a drug crisis in Punjab, India.

subTitle: Shabhana, desperate for justice, agrees to join a secret intelligence agency in exchange for their help in unmasking her friend's murderer.

title: Omerta
subTitle: Ahmed Omar Saeed Sheikh, a British terrorist of Pakistani descent, plots the kidnapping and murder of Wall Street Journal journalist Daniel Pearl.

title: Bob Biswas
subTitle: After eight years in a coma, an insurance agent returns home to his wife and son, but he has no memories of his past.

title: Mission Majnu
